      "content": "i know, i know... i've heard all that before. but a counselor can't bring him back. they can't fill the space in the bed or make the silence stop. it's not like i'm looking for a solution, it's just that everything feels so pointless. it feels like i'm just waiting for something that's never going to happen. like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life.",
